{"tid":2239555,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拍獅子山抗爭人鏈 法新社記者奪諾曼第獎","createTime":"2020-10-12T04:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T06:29:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41ff3cca334790fb5e2710fdaf43f9987ba5f9bd","tid":2239555,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/CLVAGXKSJBBHXELWZDFWTPKQSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FCLVAGXKSJBBHXELWZDFWTPKQSU%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBT%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=c568cc70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FCLVAGXKSJBBHXELWZDFWTPKQSU%2F&h=54837588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/CLVAGXKSJBBHXELWZDFWTPKQSU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n拍獅子山抗爭人鏈 法新社記者奪諾曼第獎<br />\n<br />\n表揚戰地與動盪地區記者。。。。。。。。。。。。，法新社攝影記者華萊士（Anthony Wallace）憑去年香港抗爭運動的「香港：人民反抗」（Hong Kong: A Popular Revolt）圖片報道獲獎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ixqJ23hwPE-FjIT3FcMxvMYQFrQ=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5RXUC2EOTFDARP7I26LXKIWGZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FixqJ23hwPE-FjIT3FcMxvMYQFrQ%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5RXUC2EOTFDARP7I26LXKIWGZQ.jpg&h=ba190bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■法新社「香港：人民反抗」圖片報道獲公眾之選攝影獎；圖為報道中一幅去年中秋的獅子山人鏈照片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李小龍女兒讚港示威者「如水」<br />\n<br />\n華萊士的作品獲攝影獎的「公眾之選獎」及國際評審亞軍。他其中一幅作品是去年中秋有人在獅子山組成人鏈，亮起燈光照遍山頭，展示「Free HK」標語。法新社網站登出黑衣示威者被警員制服在地上的照片。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。他憶述：「我不時感到驚訝見到在防毒面罩和護目鏡背後面孔有多年輕、甚至是青少年和20多歲的人。那一刻作為攝影師的我不想拍攝，感覺像是侵害他們。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，去年反送中示威者以一代武打巨星李小龍的「如水」哲學作為抗爭核心策略，下月是李小龍的80歲冥壽，其女兒李香凝推出的新書《Be Water, My Friend》於上星期出版，李香凝形容父親的言語和行為，隨着時間過去不斷滲透到文化之中，「看到我父親的精神以如此積極和實際方式被引導認同和理解，實在太好了」。<br />\n<br />\n提到香港示威者，李香凝指香港人愛戴和擁抱父親傳奇，並非常準確理解他的哲學含義，並以具體方式加以利用。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/英國《星期日泰晤士報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rftoEBtrQbVCSlrWN_QezD2w1xY=/886x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5HSAJQIOPVDHBF4OJ2AFW74JIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrftoEBtrQbVCSlrWN_QezD2w1xY%3D%2F886x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5HSAJQIOPVDHBF4OJ2AFW74JIY.jpg&h=04055759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■攝影記者華萊士早前憑同系列作品奪第24屆人權新聞獎。"},{"pid":"1034da5966cd2e7d1e21e9a7327377df5be60725","tid":2239555,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"談笑風生？"},{"pid":"15fad2355d48810b86f87557fed662c00238d9ae","tid":2239555,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d5fec4427708bc9f8d61cae80d08893522804c8","tid":2239555,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"如水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90d33711a9c147e0f5544104ecb284d876ea453","tid":2239555,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" cl